  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You Feel Normal.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>is a \"psx\" atmospheric horror indie game.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892270/extras/f490d86ae74bba47a573eed2f7f889f3.poster.avif?t=1732972632\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892270/extras/f490d86ae74bba47a573eed2f7f889f3.webm?t=1732972632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892270/extras/f490d86ae74bba47a573eed2f7f889f3.mp4?t=1732972632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You find yourself stranded along a lonely abandoned road desperately seeking help. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You stumble upon an old, farm-themed amusement park.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892270/extras/1541dc9fa0536c76a0a8a27d6af4aa1c.poster.avif?t=1732972632\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892270/extras/1541dc9fa0536c76a0a8a27d6af4aa1c.webm?t=1732972632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892270/extras/1541dc9fa0536c76a0a8a27d6af4aa1c.mp4?t=1732972632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you delve deeper into its depths, reality fractures into hallucinations of not your own,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >each one of them will make you feel different. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you unravel the mysteries hidden within them? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892270/extras/54f444ddb3ed08e71028430910dd37d4.poster.avif?t=1732972632\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892270/extras/54f444ddb3ed08e71028430910dd37d4.webm?t=1732972632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892270/extras/54f444ddb3ed08e71028430910dd37d4.mp4?t=1732972632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Contains:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Episodic visions (Around 30-35 minutes of gameplay)</p></li></ul>",
